name: 🌻Flower Power🌼: 🌷001🌹
description:
Clouds roll across skies like breaths in cold wind,
a murmuring coo until light breaks the cotton and falls upon soil.

A lingering shadow cuts the dawn,
the last straw cloaked amidst the corn field.

A snap dragon drowned in a sea of yellow welcomes the bumblebee resting its wings,
and a tired man rests his eyes in the back of the bus, he starts to snore.



All photography🖼️ was produced and edited by 🔥Dennis Sarovski🔥,
